        // 11 or 13 appears (because the numbers in the 11s and 13s with a 7 are also divisible
        // by 11 or 13), and that the number of times that 11 or 13 appears is equal to the
        // number of times that 11 * 11 or 13 * 13 appears.
        // In other words, the number of times that 7 appears is equal to the number of times
        // that (11 * 11) or (13 * 13) appears in the numbers less than n.
        if (n == 0) {
